Dyno Adventure (c) aresarx



                             Release 27/09/2016

         [RELEASE NOTES]

         Experience an exhilarating new sense of fun while running,
         jumping and stomping on enemies as you take control of Dyno, a
         cute dragon who has lost their family. Dyno Adventure bring you
         everything fans love about 3D platforming. Help Dyno to look for
         their children!
                          
         
         [INSTALL NOTES]
      
         [ 1 ] Unpack
         [ 2 ] Mount / burn image
         [ 3 ] Install
         [ 4 ] Copy content from 'Crack' folder and replace game dir files
         [ 5 ] Play game
         [ 6 ] If U like it, buy it!
